y>\n</html>\n```\n\n**`createListTemplate(): Template`** -- Returns a template named `'list'` that renders:\n```html\n<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html>\n<head>\n  <meta charset=\"utf-8\">\n  <title>${data.title} | ${data.siteTitle}</title>\n</head>\n<body>\n  <h1>${data.title}</h1>\n  <div class=\"list\">${content}</div>\n</body>\n</html>\n```\n\n**Barrel export** (`/workspace/src/core/index.ts`):\n```typescript\nexport { BuildEngine } from './engine.js';\nexport { createDefaultTemplate, createListTemplate } from './templates.js';\nexport type { BuildContext, ContentFile, Plugin, PluginHooks, SiteConfig, Template } from './types.js';\n```\n\n---\n\n### 5. ALL Test Files\n\n#### `/workspace/tests/core.test.ts` -- 15 tests for BuildEngine\n\nUses helpers `makeFile()` and `makePlugin()` for quick construction. Tests:\n1. **registers plugins** -- verifies `getPlugins()` length and name\n2. **registers templates** -- verifies `getTemplates()` has `'default'`\n3. **builds with default template** -- verifies `<!DOCTYPE html>`, title, content, siteTitle appear in output\n4. **builds with list template** -- verifies `<div class=\"list\">` wrapping\n5. **outputs raw content when no matching template** -- raw content passed through\n6. **calls plugin beforeBuild hook** -- boolean flag set\n7. **calls plugin transformContent hook** -- `.toUpperCase()` transform verified\n8. **calls plugin afterBuild hook** -- boolean flag set\n9. **executes plugins in dependency order** -- `b` depends on `a`, verifies `['a', 'b']` order\n10. **throws on circular dependency** -- `a<->b` cycle\n11. **throws on missing dependency** -- dependency `'missing'` not registered\n12. **applies multiple plugins transformContent in order** -- concatenation order verified (`'start [first] [second]'`)\n13. **provides shared data store** -- `ctx.data.set('key', 'value')` in `beforeBuild`, verified after build\n14. **retains file metadata through build** -- metadata, date, tags preserved\n15. **produces empty output for